Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:21.40,0:00:23.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}绑架事件总是会要求赎金
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:23.20,0:00:24.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k180}一般情况下都以钱为目的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:25.00,0:00:26.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k180}今天的事件总觉得怪怪的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:27.10,0:00:28.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}唯一看清真相的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:28.50,0:00:30.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k140}看上去是小孩  头脑却是大人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:00:30.20,0:00:32.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k170}他的名字是名侦探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:10.20,0:02:13.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}两点半啊 真是令人昏昏欲睡的时间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:21.70,0:02:23.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}怎么了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:24.10,0:02:25.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k240}快报警
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:25.10,0:02:27.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k100}救护车 快叫救护车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:32.00,0:02:35.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}已经没必要叫救护车了 是当场死亡
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:35.70,0:02:37.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}以那么快的速度驾驶不出事才怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:37.50,0:02:39.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k180}打方向盘已经来不及了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:47.50,0:02:49.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}怎么会有这么多钱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:49.30,0:02:52.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k180}真厉害 这是什么 信
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:53.20,0:02:54.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}给我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:56.20,0:02:59.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这是3千万元 没有通知警察
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:02:59.20,0:03:02.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}快把我父亲送回来 堂本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:02.50,0:03:04.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这么说来这些钱是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:05.10,0:03:08.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k260}为换回人质而准备的赎金
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:10.70,0:03:16.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}疑似绑架事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:26.50,0:03:30.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}死者是平野猛 因恐吓罪被逮捕过
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:30.80,0:03:33.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}已经比对过犯人的照片了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:33.50,0:03:37.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k270}应该是在把赎金拿回去的路上吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:37.20,0:03:41.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}如果他是独自作案的话就糟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:41.30,0:03:45.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}知道人质关押地点的人就没有了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:45.50,0:03:47.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不但如此 时间还很紧迫
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:49.10,0:03:51.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我父亲有肾病
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:51.20,0:03:53.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}每隔6小时就要服药
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:53.20,0:03:55.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}否则会有生命危险 药已经装在信封里了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:55.30,0:03:56.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}请无论如何要把药交给我父亲
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:03:59.60,0:04:03.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}就是说这个药还没有交到人质的手中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:03.20,0:04:04.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不快点交过去就会有生命危险
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:05.00,0:04:07.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k180}那么人质到底被监禁在哪里呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:08.20,0:04:12.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}绑架事件如果不知道被绑架的人是谁就没辙了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:12.30,0:04:15.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}虽然知道姓堂本 但是是哪里的堂本呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:15.40,0:04:17.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}他应该经常会去医院吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:17.80,0:04:18.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k240}为了拿药
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:27.50,0:04:30.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我们是米花电器 您买的电视机已经到了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:30.90,0:04:34.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那个 你们是不是搞错了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:35.30,0:04:37.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不会搞错的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:37.50,0:04:40.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k220}总之请你先看看定购单确认一下吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:42.10,0:04:44.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那个 我们没有买电视机
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:49.50,0:04:50.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}警察
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:51.90,0:04:52.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k240}老公
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:53.00,0:04:54.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k110}警察
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:54.80,0:04:59.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k180}好久不见 大学的学长 是我呀
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:04:59.20,0:05:00.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我是他的儿子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:01.00,0:05:02.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k180}初次见面
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:03.50,0:05:05.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k250}为什么你也来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:05.50,0:05:07.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}带着小孩子不容易被怀疑吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:09.90,0:05:11.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我们是来调查绑架事件的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:11.90,0:05:12.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:13.90,0:05:15.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}父亲他…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:16.10,0:05:21.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k220}定期到市中心的医院治疗肾衰竭的堂本先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:22.00,0:05:27.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}就是在米花中心医院做检查的堂本正三郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:27.50,0:05:28.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我们已经知道了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:29.00,0:05:30.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k150}但是你们为什么会知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:30.50,0:05:32.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k150}他们说通知了警察爸爸的性命就不保了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:34.40,0:05:36.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}情况发生了改变
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:36.40,0:05:38.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}为什么这些钱会到你们警察手里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:38.60,0:05:41.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k220}我明明已经把钱放到他们指定的地方了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:41.30,0:05:44.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k270}那个犯人骑摩托车出事故死了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.00,0:05:45.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:45.70,0:05:47.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k70}犯人他…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:48.00,0:05:49.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k230}请不要放弃
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:50.10,0:05:52.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}我们正在调查犯人的人际关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:52.40,0:05:56.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k230}不知道是否能追查到关押你父亲的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:56.10,0:05:59.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这个竟然没能交到爸爸的手中
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:05:59.20,0:06:04.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}每隔6小时 你父亲最后接受注射是什么时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:04.50,0:06:05.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}今天早上9点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:06.10,0:06:10.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k160}那么接下去是下午3点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:10.80,0:06:13.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不是已经过了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:14.70,0:06:16.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:17.50,0:06:21.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k280}并不是马上就会出状况
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:21.20,0:06:24.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}但是超过8个小时的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:24.60,0:06:26.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}就是说8小时是极限了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:27.00,0:06:30.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k240}时限就是5点 只剩下1个半小时了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:33.00,0:06:36.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你父亲是什么时候 怎么被绑架的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:36.10,0:06:38.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}还有犯人和你们是怎么接触的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:38.50,0:06:40.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k240}请详细告诉我们
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:40.60,0:06:42.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}我们家是4个人一起住
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:42.60,0:06:46.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}经营金属加工的父亲堂本正三郎
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:46.60,0:06:50.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}唯一的女儿我 我的丈夫秋成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:50.70,0:06:53.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}以及管家须藤昌代
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:53.80,0:06:56.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}今天是公司开业纪念日 大家都休息
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:57.00,0:06:59.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}所以早上起来后我们就都在家里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:06:59.70,0:07:02.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k270}我也在爸爸的公司工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:03.40,0:07:07.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}女儿和女婿将来就是继承者了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:11.70,0:07:17.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}早上9点帮爸爸注射之后我就到朋友家里去了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:21.10,0:07:25.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}今天外出是早就约好的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:26.10,0:07:28.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}然后爸爸就去散步了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:28.30,0:07:30.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k220}这是他休息日的习惯
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:30.70,0:07:33.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k240}10点左右我来到我的书房
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:33.90,0:07:36.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}有好多要整理的文件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:39.60,0:07:42.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}11点左右我在打扫浴室
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:42.40,0:07:43.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k280}然后电话响了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:43.60,0:07:45.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k120}是个年轻男子的声音
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:45.60,0:07:47.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}把电话交给家里的其他人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:49.20,0:07:50.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我是堂本
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:51.20,0:07:53.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}什么 绑架
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:54.80,0:07:59.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}也就是说 堂本正三郎是在外出散步的时候
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:07:59.30,0:08:02.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}也就是上午9点半到11点之间被绑架的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:07.30,0:08:10.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}散步有固定的路线吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:10.20,0:08:12.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k290}是的 基本一样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:12.10,0:08:13.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k190}在哪些地方呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:13.70,0:08:17.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k160}这个给你 也许能知道监禁地的线索
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:19.10,0:08:20.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我去找找
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:23.90,0:08:26.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}于是我急忙把妻子叫了回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:28.30,0:08:32.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}犯人要求的3千万日元我来想办法凑齐
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:32.40,0:08:33.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不要紧的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:34.00,0:08:36.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k160}只要付了钱爸爸就会平安地回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:37.10,0:08:38.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}交给我吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:39.70,0:08:41.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k260}拜托了 秋成
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:52.80,0:08:54.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这样就可以了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:08:55.10,0:08:57.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k230}秋成 谢谢你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:01.90,0:09:06.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}喂 把赎金…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:19.50,0:09:23.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}他说确认了钱后就把人质送回来 让我们在家里等着
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:23.60,0:09:25.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我们那么相信他的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:25.70,0:09:29.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}以防万一把药也装在信封里了 却…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:29.90,0:09:33.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}4点了 还有1小时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:33.50,0:09:36.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不要哭 爸爸一定会平安地回来的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:36.90,0:09:40.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是的 总会希望他平安吧 不管平时怎样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:50.40,0:09:52.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}毛利叔叔叫我来问一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:52.80,0:09:56.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k240}刚才的那句"不管平时怎样"是什么意思
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:09:56.70,0:10:03.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那个 老爷以前曾经给秋成先生留下痛苦的回忆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:03.60,0:10:05.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}痛苦的回忆
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:06.20,0:10:11.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k260}怎么回事 你没发现那是个圈套吗 你真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:11.70,0:10:15.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我也是为了公司才拼命地…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:15.90,0:10:19.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你终究没有成为我接班人的才能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:19.40,0:10:21.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}光看你的脸就没食欲了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:22.60,0:10:23.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:24.80,0:10:26.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k220}为什么老爷会说出那种话呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:26.80,0:10:29.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}这对秋成先生也太严厉了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:29.80,0:10:32.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}但是这种时候夫人总会帮秋成先生吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:32.90,0:10:33.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这个嘛
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:34.00,0:10:37.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k110}刚结婚的时候真是关系非常好的一对夫妻
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:38.00,0:10:40.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}但最近连光子小姐也
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:42.20,0:10:43.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你不觉得丢脸吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:43.90,0:10:47.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k170}被那样说 亏你还是个男人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:48.20,0:10:52.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}光子 为什么连你也
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:52.60,0:10:54.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}果然还是受了父亲的影响呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:55.10,0:10:57.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k250}但被绑架了就不同了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:10:57.70,0:11:02.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k260}秋成先生也很担心并且在祈祷老爷平安无事吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:02.80,0:11:06.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}所以才那么拼命地去筹钱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:11.10,0:11:14.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}大概是这样吧 和绑架案没什么关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:17.80,0:11:19.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:19.70,0:11:21.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k190}根据平野猛的朋友说
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:21.80,0:11:25.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}一周前他好像突然变得威风起来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:25.40,0:11:29.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}就是说他被人用钱雇用了吧
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:31.30,0:11:35.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}恐怕是这样 但雇用他的人是谁还不清楚
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:35.10,0:11:37.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}幕后真凶还不清楚吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:37.60,0:11:39.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k250}继续追查他的人际关系
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:40.10,0:11:43.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k250}如果知道那个人是谁就能找到监禁地的线索了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:44.20,0:11:46.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}幕后指使者另有其人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:46.20,0:11:48.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}如果是这样就很奇怪啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:48.40,0:11:49.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k220}总觉得有点奇怪 警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:49.70,0:11:50.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k130}什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:51.00,0:11:53.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k130}幕后指使者如果一直等不到取赎金的人回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:53.70,0:11:55.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k270}通常都应该会打个电话来催
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:11:56.00,0:12:00.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k230}但他为什么没来电话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:00.20,0:12:03.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}难道他准备就这样算了吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:03.30,0:12:04.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}原来如此 是有点奇怪
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:05.10,0:12:06.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k180}正是如此
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:06.60,0:12:11.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k150}既然是要钱那指使的人为什么不来追讨呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:15.00,0:12:16.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:16.20,0:12:17.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k120}光子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:17.10,0:12:20.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k90}莫非这起绑架的真正目的是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:25.90,0:12:28.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}原来是这样 这么一想的话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:29.50,0:12:31.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}怎么又来了 小家伙
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:32.00,0:12:36.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k250}秋成先生早上一直呆在自己的书房里吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:36.70,0:12:38.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是啊 有工作要做
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:38.10,0:12:40.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k140}那个时候他对你说了些什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:40.90,0:12:43.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k280}说了什么 这个
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:43.90,0:12:47.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}昌代管家 我要专心工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:47.30,0:12:48.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}就不要送茶过来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:49.80,0:12:51.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k250}果然是这样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:12:51.80,0:12:53.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}那么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:09.00,0:13:11.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}机械润滑油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:20.70,0:13:24.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我明白了 这起绑架事件的真凶
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:24.70,0:13:27.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}可是如果逼问他的话他一定会装糊涂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:27.60,0:13:29.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k290}然后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:31.00,0:13:32.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}目的不是钱
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:32.50,0:13:35.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k150}那才是犯人真正的目的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:35.90,0:13:36.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}已经4点半了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:36.60,0:13:37.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k70}还有半小时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:38.20,0:13:40.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k160}到底在哪里 监禁人质的地方
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:46.80,0:13:50.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}小鬼头 你看地图有什么用啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:50.70,0:13:54.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我在想那辆摩托打算到哪儿去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:54.20,0:13:57.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那还用说 当然是监禁人质的地方啦
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:13:57.70,0:14:01.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}所以 从拿到赎金的米花公园
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:01.60,0:14:04.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}到案发现场的这条线的前边就是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:05.70,0:14:08.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}或许如此吧 不过 柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:08.40,0:14:13.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k270}你能判断出这条延长线是10米还是100米吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:14.00,0:14:16.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这里的名字和这家人的名字…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:17.60,0:14:19.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}堂本金属
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:20.20,0:14:22.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k260}那是我家的工厂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:22.60,0:14:26.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k240}但是在半年前 东米花的新厂房建成后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:26.60,0:14:28.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那里就关闭了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:28.30,0:14:30.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k170}也就是说 是一处废弃工厂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:31.20,0:14:34.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k290}那么 那里也就不会有人去了啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:34.20,0:14:36.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}警官 作为监禁地点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:36.90,0:14:38.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k270}十分有可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:38.70,0:14:40.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k180}柯南 把地图给我
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:40.20,0:14:41.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k150}是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:41.50,0:14:43.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k130}那 爸爸他就在那个工厂里吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:44.00,0:14:45.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k250}有这个可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:46.40,0:14:48.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k240}只有15分钟了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:49.40,0:14:53.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}夫人 不到最后 就不能放弃希望
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:53.80,0:14:55.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}说得好
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:14:55.90,0:14:58.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}还剩15分钟 一定要赶上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:07.10,0:15:10.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}给我停住 时间给我停住啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:10.80,0:15:12.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:23.40,0:15:25.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}给我 让我来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:29.80,0:15:30.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:31.20,0:15:32.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k140}堂本先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:39.80,0:15:40.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:40.80,0:15:41.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k100}爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:50.10,0:15:53.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}爸爸 爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:55.00,0:15:56.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}还有呼吸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:15:57.70,0:16:00.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k270}我是高木 要救护车 地点是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:09.40,0:16:11.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}堂本先生 振作一点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:18.20,0:16:23.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}夫人要随车一起去医院了 您也请
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:23.40,0:16:24.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:27.50,0:16:29.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}您请等一下
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:30.90,0:16:31.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}为什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:32.60,0:16:34.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k170}变成沉睡的小五郎了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:34.60,0:16:36.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}毛利
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:38.90,0:16:41.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我相信堂本先生能平安脱险
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:42.00,0:16:46.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}秋成先生 你似乎在盼望着相反的结果啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:47.70,0:16:52.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}盼望着 相反的结果
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:51.10,0:16:52.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这话什么意思呢
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:52.60,0:16:57.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k150}我是在搞清楚了这宗绑架案的目的并非赎金时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:57.10,0:16:58.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}才注意到这一点的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:16:58.90,0:17:02.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k180}据柯南从管家昌代那里打听到的情报
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:03.30,0:17:06.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你和光子小姐是相爱而结婚的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:07.00,0:17:09.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}可是 入赘进入堂本家后
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:09.60,0:17:11.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k260}却被堂本先生责备
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:13.30,0:17:16.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}没有霸气 不是做继承人的料
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:16.30,0:17:19.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}开始了难熬的日子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:20.00,0:17:23.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}当然你就恨上了堂本先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:23.80,0:17:26.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}想要把他从这个世上给除掉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:28.20,0:17:29.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}怎么会
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:29.60,0:17:32.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k140}可是 你却没这个胆量
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:32.50,0:17:35.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k290}所以就计划了这次的事件
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:35.70,0:17:37.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}计划
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:37.10,0:17:40.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k140}怎么会 怎么回事 我什么都不知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:40.30,0:17:44.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不 犯人就是这个秋成先生 目暮警官
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:45.20,0:17:47.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不 这怎么可能
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:47.20,0:17:50.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}堂本先生是在散步的时候被绑架的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:50.50,0:17:52.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}当时秋成先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:52.50,0:17:54.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}我当时在书房办公
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:54.90,0:17:57.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k240}真是这样吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:57.40,0:17:59.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k250}进入了书房的你
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:17:59.70,0:18:03.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k230}昌代管家 我要专心工作
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:03.40,0:18:04.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}就不要送茶过来了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:07.40,0:18:10.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}就这样 支开了昌代管家
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:10.50,0:18:13.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你穿上了准备好的鞋子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:19.50,0:18:23.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}追上了正在散步的堂本先生 让他上了车
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:25.30,0:18:27.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你究竟想说什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:27.50,0:18:31.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k220}带我到这种地方来 你这个男人真是的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:32.20,0:18:34.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}有什么想说的就快点…
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:36.40,0:18:39.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不好 糟了 得快点回去
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:39.70,0:18:41.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我没带药
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:18:59.10,0:19:00.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}秋成先生 您的电话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:06.20,0:19:08.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}什么 绑架
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:08.80,0:19:12.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k260}就这样 你开始扮演起满脸无辜的被害者
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:14.80,0:19:16.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}当然 证据是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:16.70,0:19:18.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k190}书房的窗台上
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:18.80,0:19:21.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}应该留有和这间工厂的地板上染着的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:21.20,0:19:24.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k240}有着相同颜色的机械润滑油
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:24.50,0:19:27.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}这就是你从窗子进出过的痕迹
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:27.80,0:19:30.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}慌忙之中用来将它擦去的餐巾纸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:30.40,0:19:32.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k260}肯定就扔在那房间的某个角落里
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:32.60,0:19:34.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k220}还有更有力的证据
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:34.80,0:19:36.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k220}就是你留在地面上的进出时的脚印
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:38.80,0:19:42.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}驱车从堂本家到这里来回要花1个小时
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:42.50,0:19:44.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}所以你是有可能作案的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:44.20,0:19:48.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k170}就在你独自呆在书房里的10点到11点之间
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:49.90,0:19:53.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}的确有可能 但为什么要自己动手
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:53.90,0:19:57.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}让拿了赎金的那个姓平野的男人去做不就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:19:57.70,0:20:03.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那个男的恐怕并不知道他是在帮人绑架
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:03.60,0:20:05.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不知道他是在帮人绑架
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:05.40,0:20:08.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k180}当时他委托了平野的只有两点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:08.50,0:20:09.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}给我打个电话
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:09.50,0:20:11.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k100}上午11点和下午2点
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:12.00,0:20:15.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k250}另外一件事是从米花公园替我把一个手提箱拿来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:15.20,0:20:17.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}里边装的什么 我是什么人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:17.40,0:20:19.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k220}这些事情你最好不要知道
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:19.20,0:20:23.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k180}如果你说出了计划 就会被他抓住把柄
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:23.10,0:20:27.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}然后 你就在夫人出门去了的今天
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:27.20,0:20:28.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}实施了计划
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:28.90,0:20:31.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k170}什么 绑架了爸爸
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:31.70,0:20:34.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k280}赎金 米花公园
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:34.90,0:20:37.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}也就是说 电话是一出独角戏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:48.30,0:20:51.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}没错 要是那个平野没发生交通事故
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:51.70,0:20:53.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}不但能在之后把钱收回来
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:53.90,0:20:57.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k220}而且这个计划也就顺利地完成了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:20:57.10,0:21:00.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}警察和侦探也不会出现
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:00.60,0:21:04.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}只要在一旁装成担心堂本先生的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:04.30,0:21:06.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}等在那里就行了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:07.90,0:21:09.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}你说的没错 但是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:10.00,0:21:12.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}动机却并非是你说的那样 毛利先生
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:14.10,0:21:16.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}的确 我恨那个人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:16.90,0:21:18.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k280}想着他要是死了就好了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:19.50,0:21:20.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k260}但并不是仅此而已
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:21.70,0:21:24.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k220}我装出拼命筹钱的样子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:24.40,0:21:25.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k270}是做给光子看的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:26.70,0:21:29.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k230}只要她看到我这么拼命
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:21:30.50,0:21:32.50,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}就能重新找回她对我的爱情
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:03.90,0:23:05.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我是光子
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:05.40,0:23:08.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k150}太好了 爸爸他终于脱险了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:08.70,0:23:11.00,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}等他醒过来的时候我会对他说的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:11.10,0:23:14.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k240}你曾那样拼命地奔走
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:14.30,0:23:16.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那样地为他担心
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:16.30,0:23:20.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}爸爸他也就不会再故意气你了
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:21.80,0:23:22.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}故意的吗
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:23.40,0:23:27.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k160}爸爸他为了让你成为称职的继承人
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:27.20,0:23:29.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}故意演了一场戏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:29.70,0:23:33.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k250}因为爸爸其实很喜欢秋成的
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:33.30,0:23:35.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}只要能改掉你那过于死板的性格
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:36.30,0:23:40.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我最近也模仿着爸爸 演了一场戏
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:40.20,0:23:42.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}其实我很不情愿的 对不起
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:43.90,0:23:46.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}喂 喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:23:46.40,0:23:48.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k250}秋成 喂
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:00.50,0:24:02.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}罪犯的真正目的究竟是什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:02.70,0:24:05.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k220}还有600名乘客的性命将会怎样
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:06.20,0:24:07.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}现在毫无退路
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:07.50,0:24:09.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k130}就快要到界限的时间悬念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:10.00,0:24:12.10,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k250}剧场版新作 名侦探柯南
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:12.20,0:24:13.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k220}水平线上的阴谋
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:15.20,0:24:16.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}那部大红大紫的电影
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:16.40,0:24:17.30,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k120}初次于电视上登场
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:17.60,0:24:20.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k120}第2次发生于1千米上空的悬念
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:20.70,0:24:21.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}春假的电影特辑
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:22.00,0:24:23.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k130}名侦探柯南 银翼的魔术师
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:24.10,0:24:26.90,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k210}3月28日（周一）晚7：00播出
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:27.30,0:24:29.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}我喜欢你 新一
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:45.40,0:24:47.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k300}NEXT CONAN'S HINT
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:47.40,0:24:48.20,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k200}谁 谁在说话啊
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:48.20,0:24:49.40,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k80}石头勾玉
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:50.10,0:24:50.80,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k190}下周是
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:50.80,0:24:51.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k70}魔术的休止
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:52.10,0:24:52.60,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k130}什么
Dialogue: Marked=0,0:24:52.60,0:24:53.70,Default0,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnVerdana}{\an2}{\k50}禁欲的魔术师
